cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes a meta-learning algorithm for improving sample efficiency and generalization in reinforcement learning agents. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also applies the algorithm in the context of kick motion learning, which suggests a possible connection to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the use of RoboCup 3D Soccer Simulation domain implies a possible connection to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
